article_title: Emergency Crews On Scene Of Gas Leak In Norman - News9.com - Oklahoma City, OK - News, Weather, Video and Sports
article_text:
Emergency crews are responding to a gas leak in Norman, Oklahoma, Monday morning.

According to Norman police, a contractor was digging at 121 W. Lindsey, and hit a large gas line in the area.

Stay with us for updates.
